        <img src="https://www.anabelladentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Dentist-Bellevue-WA-AnaBella-Family-and-Cosmetic-Dentistry-Header-Logo.webp" alt="AnaBella Family & Cosmetic Dentistry" />
      </a>
      
      <nav class="nav">
        <ul class="menu">
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li class="has-submenu">
